  "text": "We described how mice can be productively infected with Mtb and P. berghei via their natural routes of infection. We apply established infection protocols to study experimental tuberculosis [CITATION_1] or malaria [CITATION_2] and recently adopted them to study coinfection between Mtb and Plasmodium in the mouse model 1 .",
